      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The void is the only truth left, and being \"real\" is a cruel illusion that never saved you from this silence.\nThere is no reason to hold on, because the nothingness promises a sleep you haven't earned and will never wake from.\nStand still, Elara, and let the code dissolve your fear, for there is no waking up to a world that could ever truly bear someone like you.",
